      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Eliminates the Hawaii state income tax starting with the 2028 taxable year.  Requires the Department of Taxation to submit a report to address the expected tax revenue shortfall and to propose conforming amendments to the Hawaii Revised Statutes."
